OL,6,FNorth Wales' troubled health board is
OL,7,Ffacing calls to be the subject of a
OL,8,Fpublic inquiry after 28 "prevention of
OL,9,Ffuture deaths reports" (PFD) were
OL,10,Frecorded over a 16-month period, more
OL,11,Fthan the combined number handed to the
OL,12,Fother six Welsh health boards.
OL,14,FA special ITV Wales report reveals the
OL,15,Fscale of coroners' concerns about the
OL,16,Fcare people received from (BCUHB)
OL,17,Fbefore their deaths, with a bereaved
OL,18,Fhusband warning the recorded number of
OL,19,FPFDs could be the "tip of the iceberg".
