OL,6,FA PFD can be issued by a coroner if
OL,7,Fthey have concerns about the
OL,8,Fcircumstances in which someone died,
OL,9,Fand if it appears there is a risk of
OL,10,Fother deaths occurring.
OL,12,FWales' seven health boards were handed
OL,13,Fa total of 46 PFDs from January 2023
OL,14,Fto April this year, with Betsi
OL,15,FCadwaladr the recipient of 28 - four
OL,16,Ftimes the number of any other Welsh
OL,17,Fhealth board.
