OL,6,FChief executive Carol Shillabeer has
OL,7,Fapologised to the families affected
OL,8,Fand admits they have been "let down",
OL,9,Fwhile the Welsh Government admits the
OL,10,Fhigh number is of "significant
OL,11,Fconcern".
OL,13,FThe troubled health board was placed
OL,14,Finto special measures in 2015, only to
OL,15,Fbe controversially taken out in
OL,16,FNovember 2020 by former health
OL,17,Fminister and current first minister,
OL,18,FVaughan Gething.
