OL,6,FIn February 2023, successor in the
OL,7,Fhealth brief, , put the health board
OL,8,Fback into special measures following
OL,9,Fconcerns being raised regarding the
OL,10,Fservice delivery, quality and safety
OL,11,Fof care and organisational
OL,12,Feffectiveness.
OL,14,FBereaved families have spoken
OL,15,Fexclusively to ITV Wales about their
OL,16,Fheartbreak at learning their loved
OL,17,Fones' deaths were not inevitable and
OL,18,Fcould have been prevented.
