OL,6,FCatherine Jones was a cardiology nurse
OL,7,Ffor Her career revolved around helping
OL,8,Fothers.
OL,10,FIn July 2013, she underwent surgery at
OL,11,Fto remove an ovarian cyst.
OL,13,FA biopsy sample from the cyst should
OL,14,Fhave been identified as borderline
OL,15,Fcancerous, which would have meant she
OL,16,Fwould have been offered surgery to
OL,17,Fremove it and, together with other
OL,18,Ftreatments, this should have been
OL,19,Fsurvivable.
