OL,6,FInstead, she was wrongly given the all-
OL,7,Fclear.
OL,9,FIn the summer of 2016, Catherine was
OL,10,Frushed back to hospital. The cancer
OL,11,Fhad spread and she died a few months
OL,12,Flater in November 2016 aged 35.
OL,14,FCoroner John Gittins
