OL,6,FHer widower David told ITV Wales:
OL,7,F"Catherine worked as a nurse in the
OL,8,Fvery board responsible for her wholly
OL,9,Fpreventable death and failed her after
OL,10,Fher death in its conduct in the
OL,11,Finvestigation into her death. That is
OL,12,Finexcusable.
