OL,12,Fwas preventable was "incredibly
OL,13,Fpainful".
OL,15,FHe said: "Although I expected it and
OL,16,Fbelieve that's the right finding based
OL,17,Fupon what I had to investigate for
OL,18,FCatherine, when you actually hear it
OL,19,Fand it's spoken in a public arena it
OL,20,Ftakes on a whole new dimension.
