OL,6,F"He was the life and soul of the
OL,7,Ffamily. Very sadly missed."
OL,9,FTwm presented to a GP in July 2021
OL,10,Fhaving experienced low moods for a
OL,11,Fnumber of years, which escalated in
OL,12,Fthe months leading up to his death
OL,13,Fafter he was a victim of an unprovoked
OL,14,Fattack in the street.
OL,16,FHe described the feeling of it
OL,17,F"hitting him like a wall" when upset
OL,18,Fand angry, and at times, thoughts of
OL,19,Fwanting to harm himself and occasional
OL,20,Fsuicidal thoughts.
