OL,6,FHe spoke with a GP over the phone and
OL,7,Fhis appointment with the mental health
OL,8,Fteam was not until 40 days after the
OL,9,Finitial referral, nearly two weeks
OL,10,Fafter the target time of 28 days.
OL,12,FAfter being seen by local primary
OL,13,Fmental health support service
OL,14,F(LPMHSS), he was deemed a "mild risk
OL,15,Fof suicide and no risk of harm to
OL,16,Fothers" and was due to be offered
OL,17,Fcounselling.
OL,19,FTwm took his own life on October 4,
OL,20,F2021 - days after his 21st birthday.
