OL,9,Fextent.
OL,11,F"In the last few months of his life he
OL,12,Fwas attacked in Pwllheli and that did
OL,13,Fhave a tremendous impact on him.
OL,15,F"As a family we were trying to get him
OL,16,Fhelp and because he was considered an
OL,17,Fadult he had to self-refer which he
OL,18,Fdid eventually.
