OL,6,FShe said: "Definitely, Twm was let
OL,7,Fdown. There is so much research about
OL,8,Fyoung lads and depression and suicide.
OL,9,FSurely that would have rung a bell in
OL,10,Fany referral.
OL,12,F"As nurses we are there to do the best
OL,13,Ffor our patients. Every treatment
OL,14,Fshould be a holistic one. It's not a
OL,15,Ftick-box exercise. Every patient
OL,16,Fshould be given that time to be
OL,17,Fassessed and if needed reassessed.
OL,19,F"So I do feel one of my colleagues had
OL,20,Flet Twm down."
