OL,6,FFollowing the inquest into Twm's
OL,7,Fdeath, coroner Sarah Riley raised
OL,8,Fconcerns about the continued staffing
OL,9,Fpressures within mental health
OL,10,Fservices, resulting in assessment
OL,11,Fdelays and waiting lists for support.
OL,13,FAt the time, the waiting list for
OL,14,FLPMHSS was between four to six months.
OL,15,FCoroner Riley said there was "no
OL,16,Fevidence" this would improve.
OL,18,FTwm's death was ruled to have been
OL,19,Fpreventable and a PFD was issued.
