OL,6,F"To be honest, I didn't quite grasp
OL,7,Fthe implication of that," said Bethan.
OL,8,F"I did know there had been so many
OL,9,Fmistakes in Twm's referral that it did
OL,10,Fhave an impact on his care.
OL,12,F"But I didn't realise how many other
OL,13,Fpeople (this affected).
OL,15,F"I already knew (Twm's death was
OL,16,Fpreventable), so for it to actually be
OL,17,Fconfirmed it was such a shock that I
OL,18,Fwas right, that Twm was not given the
OL,19,Fright level of care.
