OL,6,F"I felt guilty because I pushed him
OL,7,Fand steered him towards getting
OL,8,Fprofessional help because as a family
OL,9,Fwe felt like he needed it.
OL,11,F"I couldn't provide him with the right
OL,12,Fsafety net and for me to push and
OL,13,Fsteer him towards that help, only for
OL,14,Fhim to be let down - it made me feel
OL,15,Fguilty."
OL,17,FBut Twm and Catherine's families are
OL,18,Fnot alone. In fact, for many, their
OL,19,Fexperiences are an all too familiar
OL,20,Ftale.
