OL,6,FIt is not a coroner's role to make
OL,7,Frecommendations. Instead they draw
OL,8,Fattention to the risk so others can
OL,9,Fconsider how it should be addressed.
OL,11,FAny body issued with a PFD report has
OL,12,Fsix months to respond to a coroner's
OL,13,Fconcerns.
